    <item>
      <title>为了保护选举不受中国影响，台湾剥夺了数千选民的选举权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/protecting-taiwan-s-election-from-china-has-meant-disenfranchises-thousands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保护台湾的选举免受中国潜在的干扰是这个自治民主国家非常关心的问题，以至于多年来它一直愿意为此剥夺数十万合格选民的选举权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/protecting-taiwan-s-election-from-china-has-meant-disenfranchises-thousands</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
