      <title>布林肯敦促以色列考虑战后角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/blinken-urges-israel-to-think-of-postwar-role-as-war-grinds-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯表示，以色列必须停止削弱巴勒斯坦治理并遏制定居者暴力，这是自哈马斯战争开始以来他对总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡政府最直接的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-09/blinken-urges-israel-to-think-of-postwar-role-as-war-grinds-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 17:07:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
